      <title>国际货币基金组织计划下周召开理事会讨论新的埃塞俄比亚贷款计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/imf-plans-board-meeting-on-new-ethiopia-loan-program-next-week</link>
