      <title>标普指数涨势停滞，加拿大股市迎来“追赶交易”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/canadian-stocks-primed-for-catch-up-trade-as-s-p-rally-stalls</link>
